# 🛠 Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Deep-Learning.git
```

Move into the project

```bash
cd Deep-Learning
```

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Launch Jupyter Notebook

```bash
jupyter notebook
```

